---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Visibility Optimization for Small Business — Google, AI Search & Local — LeadFair"
  description="LeadFair optimizes how your business shows up in Google, ChatGPT, Perplexity, and local search — automatically. Search visibility, AI visibility, and local presence, all built in."
  headline="Get Found Where It Matters"
  subheadline="Google is just the start. LeadFair makes sure your business shows up in search results, AI-powered answers, and local listings — wherever your customers are looking."
  toolHref="/tools/visibility-audit"
  toolLabel="Free Visibility Audit"
  accentColor="secondary"
>
  <!-- Three Types of Visibility -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 bg-primary-50">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-dots opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-4">Three Types of Visibility</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16 text-lg">Search is changing. People don't just Google things anymore — they ask AI. LeadFair covers all three.</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="gradient-border rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover card-glow-green">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1">Search Visibility</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-secondary-600 mb-4">Show up when people Google you</p>
          <p class="text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5">The foundation. Making sure your website shows up when people search for what you offer on Google.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-sm text-text-light">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
              <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              </div>
              Website optimization & content
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
              <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              </div>
              Keyword targeting & rankings
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
              <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              </div>
              Structured data & schema markup
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="gradient-border rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1">AI Visibility</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-primary-600 mb-4">Show up when people ask AI</p>
          <p class="text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5">The new frontier. Making sure ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Google AI recommend your business when people ask for help.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-sm text-text-light">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
              <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              </div>
              AI-friendly content & structure
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
              <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              </div>
              Cross-platform presence building
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
              <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              </div>
              Citation & authority building
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="gradient-border rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover card-glow-orange">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-orange w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1">Local Presence</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-accent-600 mb-4">Show up in your area</p>
          <p class="text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5">Dominate your local market. Google Business Profile, maps, reviews, and local search — so nearby customers find you first.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-sm text-text-light">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
              <div class="icon-box icon-box-orange w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              </div>
              Google Business Profile management
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
              <div class="icon-box icon-box-orange w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              </div>
              Reviews & reputation
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
              <div class="icon-box icon-box-orange w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              </div>
              Local directory listings
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why It Matters -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 bg-gradient-green">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-16">Why This Matters Now</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover">
          <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
            <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-12 h-12 rounded-xl shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">AI Is Changing How People Find Businesses</h3>
              <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">More and more people are asking ChatGPT, Perplexity, and AI assistants for recommendations instead of searching Google. If your business isn't positioned for AI answers, you're becoming invisible to a growing segment of customers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover">
          <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
            <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-12 h-12 rounded-xl shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Most Small Businesses Haven't Adapted</h3>
              <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">While big companies invest millions in AI-era search strategies, most small businesses are still stuck on basic search optimization — if they're doing anything at all. That gap is an opportunity for businesses that move now.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 card-hover">
          <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
            <div class="icon-box icon-box-orange w-12 h-12 rounded-xl shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Built on What Actually Works</h3>
              <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">This very website is built using the same visibility principles baked into LeadFair. Fast load times, semantic HTML, structured data, authoritative content. The product uses what we've proven works.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
